# Copying Custom Settings

Copy custom settings from one bank to another, overwriting the settings in the destination bank. If the source bank has been renamed, the name will also be copied to the destination bank.

1. Navigate to **IMAGE QUALITY SETTING** in the photo menus, highlight **EDIT/SAVE CUSTOM SETTING**, and press **MENU/OK**.

   > ðŸ’¡ **Note:**  
   > To copy settings for a movie custom settings bank, navigate to **MOVIE SETTING** in the movie menus and select **EDIT/SAVE CUSTOM SETTING**.

   !Edit/Save Custom Setting Menu

2. Highlight the source bank and press **MENU/OK**.

   !Source Bank Selection

3. Highlight **COPY** and press **MENU/OK**.

   !Copy Option
